 und Beitr\u00e4ge zur schweizerischen Kirchengeschichte. Bd. III: Zwingli|url=https://archive.org/details/schmeizerkircheng03fleiuoft|year=1903|place=Luzern|publisher=J. Schill}}.\n* {{Citation|last=Gordon|first=Bruce|title=The Swiss Reformation|publication-place=Manchester|year=2002|publisher=Manchester University Press|isbn=978-0-7190-5118-0|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/swissreformation00gord}}.\n* {{Citation|last=Grob|first=Jean|title=The Life of Ulric Zwingli|url=https://archive.org/details/thelifeofulriczw00grobuoft|publication-place=New York|year=1883|publisher=Funk & Wagnalls}}.\n* {{Citation|last=Hottinger|first=Johann Jacob|title=The Life and Times of Ulric Zwingli|url=https://archive.org/details/cu31924029225831|publication-place=Harrisburg|year=1856|publisher=T.F. Scheffer}}.\n* {{Citation|last=Jackson|first=Samuel M.|title=Huldreich Zwingli, the Reformer of German Switzerland, 1484\u20131531|url=https://archive.org/details/huldreichzwingl03fostgoog|publication-place=New York|year=1900|publisher=G.P. Putnam's}}.\n* {{Citation|last=Simpson|first=Samuel|title=Life of Ulrich Zwingli, the Swiss Patriot and Reformer|url=https://archive.org/details/lifeofulrichzwin00simprich|publication-place=New York|year=1902|publisher=Baker and Taylor}}.\n\n==External links==\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{Commons category|Ulrich Zwingli|Huldrych Zwingli}}\n{{Wikisource author}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20141109151947/http://www.leben.us/volume-1-volume-1-issue-1/114-anna-reinhard Biography of Anna Reinhard, wife of Zwingli] in ''Leben'' magazine from a seminary of the [[Reformed Church in the United States]]\n* [http://www.zwingliverein.ch/ Website of the Zwingli Association and ''Zwingliana'' journal] {{in lang|de}}\n*{{prdl}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-rel}}\n{{s-new}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Antistes]] of [[Evangelical Reformed Church of the Canton of Z\u00fcrich|Z\u00fcrich]]|years=1525\u20131532}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Heinrich Bullinger]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Christian History|collapsed}}\n{{featured article}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\nThank you for reading this Wikipedia article.\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Zwingli, Huldrych}}\n[[Category:Huldrych Zwingli| ]]\n[[Category:1484 births]]\n[[Category:1531 deaths]]\n[[Category:16th-century Calvinist and Reformed theologians]]\n[[Category:Swiss Calvinist and Reformed theologians]]\n[[Category:Swiss Roman Catholic priests]]\n[[Category:History of Z\u00fcrich]]\n[[Category:Swiss military personnel killed in action]]\n[[Category:People from Toggenburg]]\n[[Category:University of Vienna alumni]]\n[[Category:16th-century Swiss writers]]\n[[Category:People from Z\u00fcrich]]\n[[Category:Critics of the Catholic Church]]\n[[Category:Former Roman Catholics]]\n", "name_user": "NotReliableForSchool", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eHistorical context)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Huldrych_Zwingli"}
